     * - `onBehalfOf` cannot be the zero address.
     * - `mintAmount` Send 0 if doesn't mint EUSD
     * - msg.value Must be higher than 0.
     *
     * @dev Record the deposited ETH in the ratio of 1:1 and convert it into stETH.
